Name: synumses-pkg-pabele
Version: 0.57
Summary: Numerical simulation package for semiconductor devices
Home-page: UNKNOWN
Author: Peter Abele
Author-email: ppabele@web.de
License: MIT
Description: **SyNumSeS** is a  package for simulating various semiconductor devices
        in one dimension. It solves the *Van Roosbroeck equations*.
        
        You can simulate:
        - pn-diodes
        - LEDs
        - MOS-diodes
        - bipolar transistors
        - solar cells
        
